<textList name="TEXT_EMV_DROPPOINT_GUARD">
	<text>As soon as you get through, you take a glance around your. Lots of ships coming in and out, tight security and heavy armaments. You are very fortunate to have proper identification.</text>
	<text>Jumping into MVPMC regions is always tense, even if it's not your first time. You see the stretching line of ships behind you as they wait to be registered in and out, and you hope that this security is good enough to delay the fleet a little.</text>
	<text>Leaving hyperspeed, you look around and gaze upon the massive security wall set up by the MVPMC. It's unlike anything you've seen, a mix of all defenses used by the many races across the stretching space. You're lucky enough to not be registered as an eligible target for those behemoth cannons.</text>
</textList>
